12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 540A, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 540A. A. Any operator of a motor vehicle who has
16 received a visual and audible signal, a flashing red light, flashing
17 red and blue lights, flashing blue and white lights, or any other
18 combination of flashing red, blue, and white lights, and a siren
19 from a peace officer driving a motor vehicle showing the same to be
20 an official police, sheriff, highway patrol or state game ranger
21 vehicle directing the operator to bring the vehicle to a stop and
22 who willfully increases the speed or extinguishes the lights of the
23 vehicle in an attempt to elude such peace officer, or willfully
24 attempts in any other manner to elude the peace officer, or who does
